
CHENNAI, JAN. 3. The additional chief metropolitan magistrate (Economic Offences) Mr.K.Balasubramanian, today posted for February 7, an `income tax case evasion case' involving Rs.1.5 crores in which Ms. N. Sasikala is an accused.
Two other accused, Mr. V. N. Sudhakaran and Ms. Ilavarasi, appeared in the court and received complaint copies. Ms.Sasikala's counsel filed a petition seeking to dispense with her appearance on health grounds. The other accused Ms.S.Ramayamma's appearance had been dispensed with by the High Court.
The case relates to the undervaluation of the consideration pertaining to the purchase of a property in Mylapore.
